      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CAWBOURNE OZZY (6) was well back throughout but attacked the line strongly to place, 2 lengths from the winner (30.05) at Wentworth Park in Grade 4/5. The form from his last run stacks up well. Good form should continue. TAW UNBOUND (2) finished eighth last time at Wentworth Park but could not have been more impressive before that in his excellent 29.71 win at Wentworth Park over 520m. Top win two back and rates a key player again. ZIPPING LILO (8) looks close to another win after finishing third from Box 2 last time (25.24) at this track. Has a very good strike-rate from this draw, with two wins from two starts. Well-placed to take this out. CARROTS (1) has strong claims after a top-three finish last time out.",
